channel.title: Need Help Remembering a Server
channel.description: Hey guys, I know I just registered, but I need help. I don't know if this is in the right section so... I remember playing on a server and it was runescape 2 or something, I'm not so sure and the hometown was Camolot, it wasn't really a pk server and they had their own site where you can buy to be a donator for 1 month, and as a donator you can spawn stuff. It's been 3 years since I played it and all I can remember is the number 37 and 52 as the server ip, it would be great if anyone can help me or tell me what happened to that server. :)
